業大麻合法化。這一消息對美股工業大麻板塊帶來了催化作用。"},{"pid":"32eb30971c8398649764af6e55fad5ee119bf46d","tid":2276881,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"大麻滾兩滾<br />\n<br />\n拜登都企唔穩"},{"pid":"2bbf8e9ea28beaed92276e6573621ac216bf77c4","tid":2276881,"uid":135258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"電車股 大麻股 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860b26cf117c411ba1df5ea4909b33c3e5d6fca3","tid":2276881,"uid":337865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"Twitter<br />\n大選倒戈搞尻侵侵<br />\n幫敗登幫到出哂面"},{"pid":"b7e40294d9d2370c333c70b50c64a4a596fe668e","tid":2276881,"uid":35763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cae2264806326bab8712933eb74e88624f7425ea","tid":2276881,"uid":6297,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"Tsla：賣碳排放配額都掂！<br />\nFSLY :tiktok 慨念股"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:35:53.000Z","msg":"Tiktok搬走曬Fsly無咩運行啦 就算佢搬翻去老美都未必會再去fsly"},{"pid":"cde2e74d3d3bb1175279ae1d337d4add4fcc25d2","tid":2276881,"uid":137694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"3800"},{"pid":"d7440c2376c96858f627c235853245e4b2bd4956","tid":2276881,"uid":269498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05709bc11fb4f8ba02a53925c09882c3c36234f6","tid":2276881,"uid":159448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"油股再唔放等破產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"Biden嘅當選政策係使用新物質能源"},{"pid":"ebdf4b864d172a7fa89ca71d3c53c2ae264a554b","tid":2276881,"uid":23988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:39:33.000Z","msg":"chips 成條 chain"},{"pid":"6d09073bf558ee714ba27834c4efd98c0d9310d9","tid":2276881,"uid":186379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"啲人之前一早入哂貨啦 準備緊出貨